Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:12.86,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:17.20,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really have to wear this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.93,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's wonderful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:21.78,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,I think it really suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:27.59,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,But... Erm... Don't you feel that... it's a bit... revealing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.11,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:35.00,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is the safest one among the swimsuits designed by Brother Clovis.{TC changed deigned to designed}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.94,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,So, hurry up and change!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.06,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I-I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:39.84,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,I can change alone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:42.52,Default,Euphemia,0000,0000,0000,,It's worn like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.24,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... Hey, don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:45.86,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Euphie, enough of your jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:49.08,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,T-The princess's swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:51.71,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:55.25,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,My son would probably feel envious if he heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:57.22,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Graston Knight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:02.45,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,I respect the fact that you picked up an orphaned boy and trained him to be a knight, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:06.31,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a bit imprudent of you to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:10.64,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Guil, you are still as old-fashioned as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:15.59,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Note: Katai(固い) can mean old-fashioned or hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:15.59,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Er... since we're talking about "hard"... Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:17.17,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Darlton...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:17.60,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:21.46,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that our mission is to be the bodyguards of the princesses, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:26.08,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're overdoing it by trying to hide a gun in your swimming trunks...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:28.41,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that obvious? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:32.69,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... To tell you the truth... it looks bizarre...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:36.92,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped... Guess I'll give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:43.82,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Cecile-san, we came here to be guards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:44.74,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:47.98,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,But is it really all right for us to be so relaxed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.42,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:55.44,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,No one would expect Princess Cornelia to be here as a surprise guest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.64,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be a need for a KnightMare to make an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.26,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Lloyd-san's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:04.11,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate that he can't come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:05.86,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.79,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That swimsuit is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.99,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gosh! Suzaku-kun, don't make fun of adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.96,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's not quite my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.97,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Suzaku-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:16.36,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:18.65,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:20.78,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.02,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:27.61,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,My family were all once local celebrities after all, so I received some invitations here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:30.26,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I brought everyone along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:31.28,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:34.03,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Lelouch! Nunnally!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.03,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:35.80,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.47,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you guys came too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:44.97,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I asked to come along, since I heard that Brother Clovis... His Highness designed the pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.41,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to swim in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:49.45,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Swim...? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:55.30,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can't move my legs, I feel more free when I'm in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.83,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, that's right... Suzaku-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:01.61,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all right with you, would you please swim together with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:05.80,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,"I'd love to"... I want to say that, but the truth is that I'm here due to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:08.71,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yup...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.07,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:15.08,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine since you'll be a distance away, but the two of you better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:16.09,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:24.71,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Today, one of the public facilities left by my brother, Clovis...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:31.60,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,This "Clovis Land" shall be opened to the public by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:40.89,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,The facility was built here on this colony as part of the effort to rouse the idea of Britannian prestige amongst the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.69,Italics,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia...!{this wasn't overlapped with the other sub to prevent a 3-liner - el}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:46.35,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,President, take a look. Lulu is staring pretty hard at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.78,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,He looks as if he's going to spring on her at anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:53.08,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,That is... Well... She's that great after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.61,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It's normal for any healthy high school male to want to cling on to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:57.75,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.45,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Erm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:03.79,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,She's great? Is Princess Cornelia really that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.33,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how I can be like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:09.14,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,That is... Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:14.37,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You'll probably need to receive various trainings from men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.85,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,P-President, what are you saying all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.11,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.91,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:21.05,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it, Nunnally?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.47,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me various things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:26.22,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can be as great as Princess Cornelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.74,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Nana-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.40,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. There might be a need for that someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.90,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.62,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.20,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even Lulu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.42,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However! I won't be gentle on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.70,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.51,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Until Brother is satisfied with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.55,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh! This is pretty amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.70,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they call a beautiful yet dangerous sibling love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.62,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! There has to be a mistake somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.06,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu!
